text-[14px]\">verified_user</span> 质量</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md max-w-md\">\n                                Surface finish tolerance deviation approaching upper limit (+0.04mm). Inspect tooling.\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md text-right\">\n<button class=\"border border-outline-variant text-on-surface px-sm py-xs rounded hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors font-label-md text-label-md h-8 mr-xs\">\n                                    Review\n                                </button>\n<button class=\"text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]\">more_horiz</span>\n</button>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- Row 3: Critical -->\n<tr class=\"border-b border-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors\">\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md\">\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-error-container text-on-error-container font-label-md text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n<span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-error\"></span> Critical\n                                </span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md font-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">09:58 AM</td>\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md\">\n<div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">Raw Material Silo 2</div>\n<div class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-[12px] flex items-center gap-xs\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]\">inventory_2</span> 库存</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md max-w-md\">\n<span class=\"font-medium\">Stock level critically low (Below 5%)</span>. 生产制造 line C may stall in 2 hours.\n                            </td>\n<td class=\"px-lg py-md text-right\">\n<button class=\"bg-primary-container text-on-primary px-sm py-xs rounded hover:bg-primary transition-colors font-label-md text-label-md h-8\">\n                                    Handle Alert\n                                </button>\n</td>